1
00:00:07,520 --> 00:00:08,920
‪SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

2
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:42,920
‪ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‪QUEEN CHU</i>‪ ON QIDIAN.COM

3
00:02:00,560 --> 00:02:02,040
<i>Dispatch Rider's Tally.</i>

4
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,520
This is how the frontier troops
tie their prisoners.

5
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:26,520
Could it be betrayal from within?

6
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:31,800
We're dispatch riders from Wangcheng.

7
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:34,960
The bandits changed into our uniforms
and went to Beicao Post House.

8
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:39,800
<i>That post house leads directly</i>
<i>to Yunzhong Prefecture.</i>

9
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:48,360
Judging by your grace and bearing,
you are no ordinary commoner.

10
00:02:48,440 --> 00:02:50,120
How did you end up in this plight?

11
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:55,320
My mother dotes on me
and wants me to look refined

12
00:02:55,920 --> 00:02:57,280
so that I might be treated
with more respect

13
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,640
once I marry into another family.

14
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:03,160
The wilderness is no place

15
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,600
for a lady to wander.

16
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:10,640
If we were to encounter bandits,

17
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,320
the dispatches you carry
are worth far more than I am.

18
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:16,280
The roads are rough at night,
and you're out here alone.

19
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,320
If you cross paths with the outlaws,

20
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:21,800
you will find yourself
completely left to your fate.

21
00:03:22,920 --> 00:03:24,880
If something actually happens to you,

22
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,160
it'll be too late to wish you hadn't.

23
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:32,800
You are a woman as well,
so if you are not afraid, why should I be?

24
00:03:39,040 --> 00:03:41,360
<i>When you speak,</i>
<i>there is no prominence in your throat,</i>

25
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,880
<i>and the angle of your radius is smooth.</i>

26
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:47,000
<i>The pauldrons of your chainmail</i>
<i>hang three cun lower than they should,</i>

27
00:03:47,080 --> 00:03:49,320
<i>which means your shoulders are narrower</i>
<i>than those of a typical male soldier.</i>

28
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,080
<i>Your knees tuck inward,</i>

29
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:53,600
<i>and when you get off a horse,</i>
<i>your toes touch the ground first,</i>

30
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,800
<i>rather than the soles of your feet.</i>

31
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:58,120
<i>It's an ingrained instinct or a woman</i>
<i>to lift her hem to shun the dirt.</i>

32
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:02,800
Your flaw lies not in your disguise
but in your habits.

33
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:05,800
Ma'am, your disguise is flawless,

34
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:09,000
but your old habits can't be faked.

35
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:12,280
You knew all along
we weren't dispatch riders?

36
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:14,880
I grew up in the army.

37
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,880
No one knows soldiers better than I do.

38
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,040
Moreover,

39
00:04:19,760 --> 00:04:22,640
you don't act like dispatch riders,

40
00:04:23,400 --> 00:04:24,440
but more like bandits.

41
00:04:26,280 --> 00:04:30,360
Since you have already seen through us,
why did you still choose to come along?

42
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:33,200
Aren't you doing the same thing?

43
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:37,520
Her vow of "My life is worth it"
still exposed us.

44
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:41,000
You saw through me long ago,
yet you still let me follow you…

45
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:44,120
because you wanted something from me.

46
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,320
You're sharp.

47
00:04:56,400 --> 00:04:57,720
But it's a pity.

48
00:04:58,440 --> 00:05:01,360
The sharp ones never live long.

49
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,160
What?

50
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,200
Are you trying to take my life?

51
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,160
At the post house,

52
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,480
I saw right through the charade
you and that woman staged.

53
00:05:14,560 --> 00:05:15,920
Yet I brought you along anyway

54
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:22,400
to see exactly what you hoped to gain
from such an elaborate ruse.

55
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,440
Put down your blade.

56
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:42,720
I said, put it down.

57
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,760
Jiu.

58
00:05:48,080 --> 00:05:49,200
Who exactly are you?

59
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:55,560
You posed as dispatch riders
to intercept intelligence

60
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,040
concerning the Northern Desert.

61
00:05:58,440 --> 00:06:00,440
Chu Ling, the Guard General,
has always been invincible.

62
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:02,920
It's impossible for a Northern Desert
squad to have exploited such a gap

63
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:05,440
unless someone leaked the dispatch.

64
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:07,720
How do you know that?

65
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,160
But if you are not closely related,

66
00:06:10,880 --> 00:06:12,200
why go to such lengths?

67
00:06:15,160 --> 00:06:16,440
Unless…

68
00:06:18,200 --> 00:06:19,200
you are from the Northern Desert.

69
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:23,560
They could never have crossed
Yunzhong Prefecture.

70
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:29,080
We are from Cangmu Stronghold.

71
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:40,080
We also suspected
that someone leaked the dispatch.

72
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,000
That is why we targeted
the dispatch riders.

73
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:45,560
We wanted to find out who at court

74
00:06:45,640 --> 00:06:48,600
is colluding with the Northern Desert
to threaten Yunzhong Prefecture.

75
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,040
Cangmu Stronghold
has always been a mystery,

76
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,240
known to but a few.

77
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:54,480
Moreover, you never meddle
in the affairs of the court.

78
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,000
Why start interfering now?

79
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:59,800
I heard during General Chu's campaign
against bandits,

80
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:02,920
he killed your former leader, Mu Mianhong.

81
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:03,840
Shouldn't you resent him?

82
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,440
Why help him now?

83
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,080
We may be nothing more than bandits,

84
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:12,960
but we do know the nation comes
before personal grudges.

85
00:07:13,880 --> 00:07:16,240
General Chu has guarded
Yunzhong for 20 years,

86
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:18,160
keeping the State of Chu in peace.

87
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:21,200
If someone in the court

88
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:24,120
colludes with the Northern Desert
to frame him,

89
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,040
the country will be in peril.

90
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,280
As will Cangmu Stronghold.

91
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:37,240
To be honest, I am Chu Ling's daughter.

92
00:07:39,280 --> 00:07:42,080
I heard my father was gravely ill
and was rushing to Yunzhong Prefecture.

93
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,760
I encountered some trouble on the road.

94
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:48,040
I had no choice but to disguise myself
and join the dispatch riders.

95
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:56,720
If you two are in trouble
and need a place to hide,

96
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,200
would you like to follow me back
to the Stronghold?

97
00:08:10,800 --> 00:08:14,000
Sir, just stopping for a quick bite
or a night's stay?

98
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,360
Have you seen any women
bound for Yunzhong Prefecture today?

99
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:19,080
There have been plenty of caravans
and women as well.

100
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:21,120
Which one are you referring to, exactly?

101
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:30,040
A runaway maid who stole from her master.

102
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:32,919
She is fair and tender,
bearing no mark of toil.

103
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:35,720
Few maids dare travel this desolate trail.

104
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:38,039
Let alone a soft-skinned lady like that.

105
00:08:41,679 --> 00:08:43,679
- Never seen one.
- Liar.

106
00:08:44,240 --> 00:08:45,080
- You've seen her.
- Officer, please calm down!

107
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,640
Where is she?

108
00:08:47,160 --> 00:08:48,320
Let me think.

109
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:51,600
I remember now. There was such a girl.

110
00:08:51,680 --> 00:08:53,160
She stayed here a couple of days ago,

111
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:55,360
claiming she was visiting kin
in Yunzhong Prefecture.

112
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,320
Later, she left with the dispatch riders.

113
00:08:57,400 --> 00:08:58,840
I don't know where she went after that.

114
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:02,000
But I do know where her mother is.

115
00:09:02,760 --> 00:09:04,080
- Her mother?
- Yes.

116
00:09:04,160 --> 00:09:06,800
Her mother hired a carriage
and went back to the village herself.

117
00:09:07,520 --> 00:09:09,240
From that livery stable
three li north of here.

118
00:09:22,080 --> 00:09:23,840
- Come back!
- No, I won't…

119
00:09:23,920 --> 00:09:25,040
- Officer.
- Despicable wretch!

120
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,320
You owe me a fortune!

121
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:27,440
You…!

122
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:34,560
A few days ago,
did a girl named Fu come through here?

123
00:09:35,240 --> 00:09:37,120
Officer, what do you mean?

124
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:40,680
We get so many girls passing through,
how could I remember every name?

125
00:09:40,760 --> 00:09:41,800
Don't play dumb.

126
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:46,240
She paid you to put on an act
and then left with the dispatch riders,

127
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:48,240
- didn't she?
- Yes.

128
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:50,800
She tricked those dispatch riders,
and they headed for Yunzhong.

129
00:09:58,160 --> 00:09:59,400
Good.

130
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:02,400
Seems you are destined to die.

131
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,440
This forest reeks of something foul.

132
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:23,480
The traps and mechanisms
must be over a hundred.

133
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:28,480
This is far too elaborate
for a mere stronghold of bandits.

134
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:31,720
Are they truly trustworthy?

135
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:34,400
I'm not sure.

136
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,840
Then why did you insist on coming?

137
00:10:41,480 --> 00:10:42,720
Madam Ge wasn't lying.

138
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:45,960
Her story matches perfectly
with what I knew of the past.

139
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:51,160
It seems Cangmu Stronghold wasn't always
at odds with my father,

140
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,600
despite what rumors say.

141
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:54,960
Tie Ying is no fool.

142
00:10:55,040 --> 00:10:57,440
My tricks will only last
half a day at most.

143
00:10:58,080 --> 00:10:59,480
We are outnumbered.

144
00:10:59,560 --> 00:11:00,600
A head-on fight is not the best course.

145
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:03,080
We'd better seek refuge
in Cangmu Stronghold

146
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:05,360
and plan our next move
after scouting the truth.

147
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:10,560
So, you're still gambling.

148
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:13,760
I dared to risk
only because you stood by me.

149
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,960
Don't get cocky.

150
00:11:31,680 --> 00:11:33,320
Last night, you were clearly defenseless,

151
00:11:34,040 --> 00:11:35,720
yet you still chose
to provoke the bandits.

152
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:39,280
Do you realize,
if I'd been a moment later,

153
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,800
you'd be a corpse by now?

154
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:42,800
If they wanted me dead,

155
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:46,000
they would have struck
when I exposed Madam Ge's disguise.

156
00:11:47,680 --> 00:11:48,880
Is that why you risked your life?

157
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:54,520
Her taking men disguised
as dispatch riders to steal the dispatch

158
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:58,320
isn't to hurt my father
but to uncover the truth.

159
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:01,680
In other words, she truly is helping him.

160
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:03,840
Aren't you afraid

161
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,160
you've jumped out of the frying pan
and straight into the fire?

162
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:11,320
Isn't that just what we do every day?

163
00:12:24,560 --> 00:12:26,080
CANGMU STRONGHOLD

164
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:27,720
- Ge is back.
- Ge's returned.

165
00:12:27,800 --> 00:12:28,840
- Ge.
- Madam.

166
00:12:28,920 --> 00:12:29,960
- Madam is back.
- Ge.

167
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:32,240
- Ge.
- Welcome back.

168
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,240
Ge.

169
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:34,280
Let me take that.

170
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,520
Ge.

171
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,280
Aunt.

172
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:42,360
- Laosan, we have guests.
- Coming.

173
00:12:44,600 --> 00:12:47,280
This is my younger brother, Ge Laosan,
leader of Cangmu Stronghold.

174
00:12:48,040 --> 00:12:49,240
Greetings, Mr. Ge.

175
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:50,800
‪GE LAOSAN, CANGMU STRONGHOLD

176
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:52,480
Xiaoman.

177
00:12:52,560 --> 00:12:53,480
‪XIAOMAN, CANGMU STRONGHOLD

178
00:12:54,320 --> 00:12:55,240
Take a seat.

179
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:57,920
Why'd you bring two strangers back?

180
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,000
We need a place to lie low for a while.

181
00:13:01,080 --> 00:13:02,080
Lie low?

182
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:05,200
How should I address you two?

183
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:07,760
He's Jiu. I'm Fu.

184
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,680
Fu.

185
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:11,720
Good name.

186
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:14,040
Sounds like good fortune.

187
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:19,800
Madam Ge, there's something I need to ask.

188
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:21,560
I know what it is.

189
00:13:22,160 --> 00:13:23,200
Don't worry.

190
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:25,640
You saw it for yourselves on the way in.

191
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:29,520
We are known as Cangmu Stronghold,
hidden deep within these woods.

192
00:13:30,160 --> 00:13:31,520
There's a saying down the mountain,

193
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:34,200
"Once you go deep into Cangmu Forest,
there's no way out."

194
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:37,920
This forest is vast and deep,
a fortress built by nature itself.

195
00:13:38,000 --> 00:13:40,160
And we have all those hidden mechanisms
and traps.

196
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:43,760
With bamboo nets overhead
and vine-traps underfoot,

197
00:13:43,840 --> 00:13:45,360
all life is barred from entry,

198
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,800
be it human or beast.

199
00:13:46,880 --> 00:13:49,720
Here, you're safer than anywhere outside.

200
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:52,480
If this place is so secret,

201
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:55,520
how could you trust us enough
to let us in?

202
00:13:56,520 --> 00:13:57,480
Aren't you afraid?

203
00:13:57,560 --> 00:13:59,840
We value fate above all.

204
00:13:59,920 --> 00:14:02,160
I've trusted you, so I won't question it.

205
00:14:06,160 --> 00:14:08,640
Xiaoman, see to our guests.

206
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:11,680
Once things calm down out there,
you can resume your journey.

207
00:14:13,640 --> 00:14:14,480
My gratitude, ma'am.

208
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,440
Apologies for the intrusion.

209
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:19,680
No trouble at all.

210
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:21,320
This way, please.

211
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:26,480
Have a good rest.

212
00:14:31,440 --> 00:14:32,360
She…?

213
00:14:48,800 --> 00:14:50,080
Mr. Tie!

214
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:51,680
Mr. Tie.

215
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:55,960
Mr. Tie. Something's wrong.

216
00:14:56,040 --> 00:14:57,600
The dispatch riders we were pursuing,
along with the Grand Princess,

217
00:14:57,680 --> 00:15:00,280
have vanished without a trace
near Cangmu Stronghold.

218
00:15:01,160 --> 00:15:02,280
The men we dispatched in pursuit

219
00:15:02,360 --> 00:15:04,680
were all slain
by the bandits of the stronghold.

220
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:06,960
Cangmu Stronghold?

221
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:11,880
I promised His Highness
to bring back Chu Zhao's head.

222
00:15:13,640 --> 00:15:15,400
Hear my command.

223
00:15:15,480 --> 00:15:17,720
Pick up the pace
and march into Cangmu Forest.

224
00:15:17,800 --> 00:15:19,680
Leave no one alive.

225
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:24,360
I'd like to see what these remnants think
they can do to shield her.

226
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:39,000
They offered you shelter,
and now you're raiding their armory?

227
00:15:39,080 --> 00:15:40,280
Cangmu Forest is vast and deep.

228
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:42,640
They seem hospitable enough,

229
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:45,760
but how could we truly rest easy
without investigating first?

230
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:47,840
I didn't realize,

231
00:15:47,920 --> 00:15:50,200
though new to the jianghu,
you would think further ahead than I.

232
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:52,960
Look at this.

233
00:15:55,000 --> 00:15:56,320
Careful.

234
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:03,520
Seven modifications to the mechanism.

235
00:16:03,600 --> 00:16:07,280
Range increased by two zhang,
with less recoil.

236
00:16:08,600 --> 00:16:11,200
These are modified crossbows
the frontier troops used

237
00:16:11,280 --> 00:16:12,400
against the Northern Desert.

238
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,640
How do you know?

239
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:16,120
Back when I was in the army,

240
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:18,320
I modified over 200
of these crossbows for the General.

241
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:22,320
Mu Mianhong was killed
by my father, after all.

242
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:26,200
So why would her stronghold
have weapons from the frontier troops?

243
00:16:26,800 --> 00:16:27,760
It's not just that.

244
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:30,360
While searching for you,

245
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,120
I saved a dispatch rider
who had been kidnapped by Madam Ge.

246
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,640
<i>The knots used to tie him up</i>

247
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:37,600
<i>were standard frontier troop rigging.</i>

248
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:39,880
You mean…?

249
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,080
Perhaps

250
00:16:41,840 --> 00:16:44,280
your father wasn't here
to suppress bandits.

251
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,880
What are you implying?

252
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:48,680
- Are you suggesting my father…?
- Wait for me.

253
00:16:57,760 --> 00:16:58,760
I won't be long.

254
00:17:55,600 --> 00:17:56,720
Your Highness,

255
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,160
this feels a little too personal.

256
00:18:01,320 --> 00:18:02,920
Back when I left the Capital,

257
00:18:03,000 --> 00:18:05,400
who was it that swore
to guard the imperial city for me?

258
00:18:12,280 --> 00:18:15,200
I know it's because you care about me.

259
00:18:18,280 --> 00:18:21,920
But Xie Yanfang wouldn't release you
without expecting something in return.

260
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,680
What's the situation at court?

261
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:27,920
He'll look after Yu.

262
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:32,120
But he needs the Grand Princess Token
to keep Deng Yi on a leash.

263
00:18:34,560 --> 00:18:35,960
So I handed it over.

264
00:18:43,520 --> 00:18:44,600
Indeed.

265
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,160
Your brother

266
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:49,760
has never been one to show his hand
without a guaranteed win.

267
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:52,520
If you're not in the Capital,

268
00:18:53,280 --> 00:18:56,120
he's the only one who can keep Yu safe.

269
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,880
Your wounds have yet to heal.

270
00:19:02,960 --> 00:19:04,000
You need proper rest.

271
00:19:07,800 --> 00:19:08,920
Just get some sleep.

272
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:28,840
They… only gave us one room?

273
00:19:33,960 --> 00:19:34,920
I insisted on this.

274
00:19:37,440 --> 00:19:39,000
With such grave injuries,

275
00:19:40,440 --> 00:19:42,000
you need to stay close to me.

276
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:44,440
Or how am I supposed to protect you?

277
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:01,800
And how will you protect me exactly?

278
00:20:22,920 --> 00:20:24,040
It's a cold night.

279
00:20:25,960 --> 00:20:27,320
Your wounds won't heal if you freeze.

280
00:20:32,560 --> 00:20:33,640
Keep warm.

281
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:50,680
Are you out of your mind?

282
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:54,920
You knew who she was
and you still brought her here?

283
00:21:08,080 --> 00:21:09,800
They're not to be trifled with.

284
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:14,640
Xiao Xun's ambushes
always have a deeper kill.

285
00:21:15,560 --> 00:21:17,960
That guard at the gate
sent word in the White Wolf tongue,

286
00:21:19,080 --> 00:21:20,640
saying the pursuers
have all been eliminated.

287
00:21:21,560 --> 00:21:25,280
If they were with Xiao Xun,
why would they kill their own?

288
00:21:26,120 --> 00:21:27,600
I didn't know you could speak that tongue.

289
00:21:28,600 --> 00:21:31,240
My father taught me
when we were in the desert.

290
00:21:33,400 --> 00:21:39,280
No one knows that except him.

291
00:21:40,160 --> 00:21:41,800
But what if it's all just an act?

292
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:44,680
Xiao Xun's men have no reason
to slaughter their own.

293
00:21:45,280 --> 00:21:48,560
Given how cautious Deng Yi is,

294
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:51,960
he'd never trust a band of bandits
who still answer to their old master.

295
00:21:52,040 --> 00:21:53,120
He wouldn't trust them.

296
00:21:54,080 --> 00:21:56,520
And Xie Yanfang? Even less likely.

297
00:21:58,440 --> 00:22:01,360
Whether Madam Ge and the others respect
my father or fear him,

298
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:04,080
at the very least,

299
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:09,200
my father never bore them any ill will.

300
00:22:10,280 --> 00:22:14,480
I still find it hard to believe
they've suddenly turned into saints.

301
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:19,240
Are you willing to take a gamble with me?

302
00:22:20,200 --> 00:22:21,680
What if we lose?

303
00:22:31,040 --> 00:22:33,040
At least on the road to the afterlife,

304
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,560
you'll keep me company.

305
00:22:41,880 --> 00:22:42,800
TAIJI HALL

306
00:22:42,880 --> 00:22:46,120
Recently, our dispatch riders
were ambushed near the Beicao Post House.

307
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:48,800
Investigations confirm that this was
the work of the Cangmu Stronghold.

308
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:51,800
This is an absolute outrage.

309
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:53,200
- Utterly preposterous.
- Indeed.

310
00:22:53,280 --> 00:22:55,880
Chu Ling's leniency
allowed these bandits to flourish.

311
00:22:55,960 --> 00:22:58,720
Now, the remnants of that stronghold
have the audacity

312
00:22:58,800 --> 00:23:01,720
to pose as our dispatch riders
to steal vital military intelligence.

313
00:23:02,320 --> 00:23:03,760
Your Majesty, I implore you

314
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:05,480
to issue a decree for a full investigation

315
00:23:05,560 --> 00:23:07,080
and ensure that justice is served.

316
00:23:07,920 --> 00:23:10,520
General Chu marched against the bandits
on imperial command.

317
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:13,560
When the bandit leader, Mu Mianhong,
took her life by leaping from the cliff,

318
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:14,840
he refused to harm
even the women and children

319
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:16,240
remaining in the stronghold.

320
00:23:16,760 --> 00:23:20,680
To think that such benevolence
is being wielded against him?

321
00:23:20,760 --> 00:23:21,920
Well…

322
00:23:22,560 --> 00:23:24,960
Your Majesty, an urgent report
has just arrived.

323
00:23:25,040 --> 00:23:26,760
The Northern Desert
dispatched an envoy to Yunzhong,

324
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:28,720
only for General Chu
to execute him on the spot.

325
00:23:29,320 --> 00:23:31,920
Tensions between the two states
are already high.

326
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:33,560
What are we to do now?

327
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:36,720
Even in war,
one does not kill a messenger.

328
00:23:36,800 --> 00:23:40,040
This act will surely incite them
to take up arms.

329
00:23:40,120 --> 00:23:42,280
The charge of leniency toward bandits
might be overlooked,

330
00:23:42,360 --> 00:23:45,520
but inciting a war is unpardonable.

331
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:48,960
First, they breached our frontier.

332
00:23:49,040 --> 00:23:51,600
Then, their envoy infiltrated
the General's tent

333
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,680
with a secret letter at night.

334
00:23:54,320 --> 00:23:56,080
If that isn't espionage, then what is?

335
00:23:56,160 --> 00:23:57,880
Mr. Deng is correct.

336
00:23:58,640 --> 00:24:00,600
The General has commanded
the frontier troops for decades,

337
00:24:00,680 --> 00:24:01,720
with his defenses impregnable.

338
00:24:01,800 --> 00:24:03,640
If they nearly faltered last time,

339
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:05,480
it must be because a spy
leaked our positions.

340
00:24:06,520 --> 00:24:09,680
Desperate times demand desperate measures.

341
00:24:10,280 --> 00:24:11,280
According to our laws,

342
00:24:11,360 --> 00:24:14,520
when a threat is imminent and unclear,
one may act first and report thereafter.

343
00:24:15,360 --> 00:24:17,080
So how can General Chu be blamed?

344
00:24:20,000 --> 00:24:22,880
Your Majesty, General Chu
is advanced in years.

345
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:25,520
As the frontier defenses
have seen repeated breaches,

346
00:24:25,600 --> 00:24:27,760
I beg Your Majesty
to appoint another worthy general.

347
00:24:29,680 --> 00:24:31,840
These concerns are not without merit.

348
00:24:31,920 --> 00:24:35,120
As the Northern Desert stirs
with ambition, we must fortify

349
00:24:35,840 --> 00:24:39,000
the frontier in anticipation of conflict.

350
00:24:40,480 --> 00:24:42,360
As for the selection of a successor,

351
00:24:44,760 --> 00:24:46,680
it remains a matter
for His Majesty's judgment.

352
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:49,640
The General has held Yunzhong
for 20 years.

353
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:52,520
Each time the enemy dared to invade,
they were repelled in ignominious defeat.

354
00:24:53,640 --> 00:24:55,800
In your candidate list,

355
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:59,440
how many can truly rival
his illustrious record?

356
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:01,800
A commander of such stature
is not cultivated overnight.

357
00:25:01,880 --> 00:25:06,320
Yet, the security of the frontier
cannot be staked upon a single individual.

358
00:25:07,880 --> 00:25:09,280
Mr. Xie, please set your mind at rest.

359
00:25:09,360 --> 00:25:12,440
I shall confer with the ministers

360
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:16,680
to select the most fitting candidate
for Yunzhong Prefecture

361
00:25:17,560 --> 00:25:19,520
to alleviate the General's burdens.

362
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:29,000
<i>What a masterful move he's played.</i>

363
00:25:47,080 --> 00:25:48,000
This is…

364
00:25:49,200 --> 00:25:50,040
Sand Fox Whistle.

365
00:25:50,120 --> 00:25:51,400
That's right.

366
00:25:52,160 --> 00:25:54,080
This is a frontier troop alert
for cavalry raids.

367
00:25:56,320 --> 00:25:57,840
Stubborn, aren't you?

368
00:25:57,920 --> 00:25:58,920
BROTHERS IN ARMS, WISE IN DEED

369
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:00,120
Talk.

370
00:26:00,680 --> 00:26:01,760
If you won't,

371
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:05,600
I'll chop you to pieces
and feed you to the wolves in the hills.

372
00:26:05,680 --> 00:26:08,200
- Throw him to the wolves!
- Throw him to the wolves!

373
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:09,320
Talk or not?

374
00:26:12,120 --> 00:26:13,240
What are you doing here?

375
00:26:14,160 --> 00:26:15,560
I'm in the middle of something.

376
00:26:15,640 --> 00:26:16,480
Don't mind me.

377
00:26:17,160 --> 00:26:18,400
Leave him to me.

378
00:26:27,600 --> 00:26:29,520
- That's pretty brutal.
- Indeed.

379
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:31,280
- Listen to the scream.
- Right.

380
00:26:32,160 --> 00:26:33,360
What is he doing?

381
00:26:33,440 --> 00:26:36,280
That's brutal.

382
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:38,760
Tell me about it!

383
00:26:38,840 --> 00:26:40,640
Brutal…

384
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:47,160
Didn't see that coming. He's good.

385
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:51,880
- Well?
- He talked.

386
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:55,960
They entered Cangmu Forest yesterday
and located Cangmu Stronghold.

387
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:58,040
Their men will arrive tonight.

388
00:26:58,120 --> 00:26:59,120
We should prepare in advance.

389
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:01,360
I need to tell my sister.

390
00:27:30,080 --> 00:27:34,840
Did you learn those interrogation tricks
from my father's army?

391
00:27:36,760 --> 00:27:37,680
Not really.

392
00:27:39,400 --> 00:27:41,240
He advocated
for the humane treatment of captives.

393
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:44,000
He'd never have used torture on them.

394
00:27:49,000 --> 00:27:50,080
Are you not afraid anymore?

395
00:27:50,840 --> 00:27:52,120
Why would I?

396
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:54,560
I grew up in military camps.

397
00:27:54,640 --> 00:27:56,360
I've seen my share

398
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:58,520
of slaughter and bloodshed.

399
00:28:06,880 --> 00:28:08,640
That is no blessing.

400
00:28:10,120 --> 00:28:11,280
Better to have never seen it at all.

401
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:20,640
But in this life, who truly has a choice?

402
00:28:22,040 --> 00:28:25,080
I have no desire to kill,
yet they come for my life.

403
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:32,880
I told you I kill
just so I can stay alive.

404
00:28:35,000 --> 00:28:38,280
I want to live to see my father again.

405
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:40,520
I will do the killing for you.

406
00:28:46,720 --> 00:28:48,320
Hey. The ones after them

407
00:28:48,400 --> 00:28:51,520
belong to Xiao Xun,
heir to the Lord of Xiaonan.

408
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,960
A humble meal

409
00:28:55,200 --> 00:28:56,760
in a humble place.

410
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,760
I hope Your Highness can forgive me.

411
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:22,680
You are the Grand Princess?

412
00:29:23,600 --> 00:29:26,760
No. You were supposed to marry
the heir to the Lord of Xiaonan.

413
00:29:28,680 --> 00:29:29,840
So you eloped with this man?

414
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,480
Xiao Xun deceived me.

415
00:29:41,360 --> 00:29:42,880
Everything he wanted,

416
00:29:42,960 --> 00:29:46,040
from the very start,
was my father's command over the army.

417
00:29:47,280 --> 00:29:48,640
But I won't let him have it.

418
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,120
Never ever.

419
00:29:52,880 --> 00:29:54,760
You're Chu Ling's daughter.

420
00:29:55,600 --> 00:29:58,000
Did he ever tell you who your mother was?

421
00:30:06,520 --> 00:30:09,200
Mr. Ge, you take quite an interest
in Yunzhong Prefecture.

422
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:12,480
You even know every detail
of my betrothal.

423
00:30:13,160 --> 00:30:18,480
No wonder this stronghold
bears the marks of frontier troops.

424
00:30:28,680 --> 00:30:32,480
Since we're speaking so frankly,
ma'am, you might as well tell the truth.

425
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:35,680
What really happened when my father went

426
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,960
to Cangmu Stronghold?

427
00:30:39,840 --> 00:30:41,360
Nothing much.

428
00:30:42,400 --> 00:30:47,040
It's just
that General Chu killed our former leader.

429
00:30:47,720 --> 00:30:49,320
Then why do you still care
about him so much?

430
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:53,720
Don't you want to avenge your leader?

431
00:31:00,960 --> 00:31:04,960
Back then, word got out
that we were raiding the frontier,

432
00:31:05,040 --> 00:31:06,840
so General Chu came to eradicate us.

433
00:31:07,640 --> 00:31:10,720
But after killing the former leader,
he realized it was all a misunderstanding.

434
00:31:11,880 --> 00:31:13,920
So he stepped in to resettle
the rest of us.

435
00:31:14,520 --> 00:31:16,000
Everything you see now

436
00:31:16,080 --> 00:31:19,600
is just your father's guilt
and his way of making amends.

437
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:22,520
- But…
- The debt has been settled.

438
00:31:23,920 --> 00:31:25,360
There's no point bringing it up anymore.

439
00:31:29,080 --> 00:31:30,520
You've had a long journey.

440
00:31:30,600 --> 00:31:31,640
Why don't you try to get some rest?

441
00:31:32,360 --> 00:31:33,760
I'm right here if you need anything.

442
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:53,440
They aren't like ordinary bandits.

443
00:31:54,320 --> 00:31:58,160
Their story about the General's campaign,
how he supposedly killed the innocents,

444
00:31:58,800 --> 00:32:00,400
is rather flimsy.

445
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:04,000
Largely fiction, with a grain of truth.

446
00:32:06,320 --> 00:32:09,400
But I do believe my father
genuinely wanted to protect this place.

447
00:32:10,360 --> 00:32:15,000
And I'm certain they mean no harm to us.

448
00:32:15,600 --> 00:32:17,080
As for the rest…

449
00:32:17,600 --> 00:32:19,240
Everyone has secrets.

450
00:32:20,080 --> 00:32:23,920
When they'll finally come to light,
that's just a matter of fate.

451
00:32:30,840 --> 00:32:32,080
Wangcheng is just ahead.

452
00:32:32,160 --> 00:32:35,080
Past it lies Yunzhong Prefecture.

453
00:32:36,960 --> 00:32:38,680
Once we deal with Xiao Xun's men,

454
00:32:41,800 --> 00:32:43,080
you'll finally see your father.

455
00:32:45,440 --> 00:32:46,440
I know.

456
00:32:48,040 --> 00:32:49,120
I know this road

457
00:32:51,160 --> 00:32:52,400
all too well.

458
00:32:58,880 --> 00:32:59,920
<i>Back then,</i>

459
00:33:01,160 --> 00:33:03,000
<i>this was the exact path I took</i>

460
00:33:04,440 --> 00:33:05,840
<i>to be away from my father,</i>

461
00:33:07,960 --> 00:33:09,360
<i>Yunzhong Prefecture,</i>

462
00:33:10,880 --> 00:33:12,920
<i>and everything that held me dear,</i>

463
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,920
<i>only to fall</i>

464
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:18,480
<i>into the mire of eternal doom.</i>

465
00:33:43,360 --> 00:33:44,200
Jiu.

466
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:48,640
If we had a second chance at life,

467
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:52,360
would anything actually change?

468
00:34:01,760 --> 00:34:02,760
A second chance

469
00:34:04,640 --> 00:34:06,040
<i>at life…</i>

470
00:34:06,120 --> 00:34:06,760
GRACE AND BENEVOLENCE

471
00:34:09,159 --> 00:34:11,800
<i>‪Jiu, from now on, you have</i>
<i>‪a home here at Xie Residence.</i>

472
00:34:12,719 --> 00:34:14,639
<i>‪Mother!</i>

473
00:34:35,080 --> 00:34:36,239
Perhaps it wouldn't change a thing.

474
00:34:38,159 --> 00:34:39,440
But for me,

475
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:42,360
things are already different.

476
00:34:45,719 --> 00:34:49,840
Remember that dream I told you about?

477
00:34:51,440 --> 00:34:52,920
<i>At the very end,</i>

478
00:34:54,120 --> 00:34:57,320
<i>someone killed Xiao Xun for me.</i>

479
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:01,680
<i>Do you know who it was?</i>

480
00:35:03,840 --> 00:35:05,200
It was you.

481
00:35:13,640 --> 00:35:18,120
You killed him and avenged my family.

482
00:35:22,360 --> 00:35:23,600
But this time,

483
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:28,120
I have to do it myself.

484
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:31,440
Though fear may still echo in my chest,

485
00:35:33,160 --> 00:35:35,760
and a crumbling cliff awaits my next step,

486
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:37,280
nothing in this world

487
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:41,840
will hold me back.

488
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:20,160
Whatever you fear in the days to come,

489
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:25,960
whatever that dream may be, real or not,

490
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:28,920
face it,

491
00:36:30,680 --> 00:36:31,640
grasp it,

492
00:36:33,080 --> 00:36:34,280
and conquer it.

493
00:36:40,840 --> 00:36:42,520
And the fear will leave you.

494
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:44,920
I'm not terrified.

495
00:36:47,320 --> 00:36:48,760
My father and I

496
00:36:50,680 --> 00:36:52,480
will survive.
